ownedRule.name: auditability: all messages received from or sent to external parties is logged

ownedComment.body: Register a new member such that the member may make use of the library. The member details are persisted and a loan account is opened for the member.

mdElement.text: This association implies that an identifier for the loan account will be provided - e.g. the loan account number, a library card which is associated with the loan account or something like that.
